Package com.percyvega.motionpoint.crm

Domain classes for supporting MotionPoint in storing customer information.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Company
    Company encapsulates the abstraction of a MotionPoint corporate customer.
    Website
    Website encapsulates the abstraction of the website of a MotionPoint corporate customer.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CompanyImpl
    CompanyImpl encapsulates the implementation of a MotionPoint corporate customer.
    CompanyUtil
    CompanyUtil contains the utility functionality to support Company (and Website).
    CompanyUtilTest
    CompanyUtilTest contains the unit tests that verify the functionality of CompanyUtil.
    InvalidCompanyPhoneNumberTest
    InvalidCompanyPhoneNumberTest contains the negative unit tests that verify the functionality of Company's setPhoneNumber
    ValidCompanyPhoneNumberTest
    ValidCompanyPhoneNumberTest contains the unit tests that verify the functionality of Company's setPhoneNumber
    WebsiteImpl
    WebsiteImpl encapsulates the implementation of the website of a MotionPoint corporate customer.
    WebsiteUrlTest
    WebsiteUrlTest contains the unit tests that verify the functionality of Website's setUrl.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Language
    Language is an enumeration representing the list of available Languages for websites.
